Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  你的母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤乃鹭全体的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能是你这样一个小鬼的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掂掂自己份量吧  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生才是  果然椅子不能消除疲劳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就代替我去床上…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和小民两个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小民可能也不讨厌那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里说不定能睡得很舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生有女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…现在还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很擅长和女性相处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得你是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请相信自己  雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  还以为你是因为伯母的事才沮丧的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来根本原因是男朋友的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我要是回应得正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说不定已经是我男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就是不相信呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然嘴上很会说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那张脸表达得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去睡了  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要诱拐松前皋月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松前皋月不打算去喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以决定用武力绑她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是松前皋月工作的大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从车站这条路线考虑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个小巷里埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将她一口气带走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送车辆也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也有三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也应该能封住松前皋月的蛮力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  彻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以  但有条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫孝一的人也一起带去喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是让我们参加诱拐的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  民子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在绪花把孝一带来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们先去观光东京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是早餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了这种纸片一样的面包也毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京可是存在着许多被称为名店的馆子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为客人  用舌头去记忆也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拨打的电话不在服务区…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带阿孝一起走什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该用什么表情去见他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一个人又诱拐不了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？为什么交换条件是阿孝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想…不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不仔细想也很奇怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系不上诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去过打工的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不在也没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生也会原谅我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绪花…小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有那个意思的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把他解放吧  解放孝一君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  解放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说得真是难听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没把阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是打算诱拐一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嘀嘀咕咕说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的解放是指心理上的解放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提  我们现在所坐着的长椅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我向孝一君告白的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在交往了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  暂时还没有给我答复
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那算什么  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我觉得她大概是没有那个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我擅自在等她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也习惯等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是我不照顾着她  那家伙总是让人不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在玩弄孝一君的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也对阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为异性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作为人类…什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算说这些打发人的话么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是如何喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人…作为一个生物喜欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十岚小姐  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的你就自己判断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你再践踏孝一君的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一弯  就前面往右转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像约会一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别剩下一粒饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通过五分熟的火候来强调口感的变化么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是考虑到上菜的时机和余热的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吐了  就算吐了还得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易来了东京
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名店的味道必须一一记住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花的事只是顺便  顺便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所居住的  阿孝也在的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经很讨厌的无聊的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女生…是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样认真  直爽的说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能直视着对方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:10:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要到旅馆里去生活  感觉突然很有戏剧性了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说有我们出演的电视剧的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反面角色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（来电：阿孝）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一号线电车车门即将关闭 请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  害你打了这么多次电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的人联系过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你来过书店了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧？不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀…就和那时的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在之前放假的时候  去你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找人而闯入婚礼现场的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想去一趟喜翠庄的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看你挺忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花？能听见么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反面角色…就是我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要带妈妈回喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此必须把阿孝也带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就给阿孝打了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候明明已经被阿孝所救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这次又想让阿孝来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着加油吧  雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直只想着自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些照顾着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为自己加油的人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是最差劲的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不用来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝一直都照顾着最差劲的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此  那个时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说了下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他却没有回答下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有下次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最想哭的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…寿司呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来抓个什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静不下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花她和其他男性见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明离开还不到半年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却觉得是那么的怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独喜欢这个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像雪洞一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎一直通向未来的灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种人都有自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝也有  妈妈也有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有他们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我伤害了阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝为了我而雪愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被妈妈伤害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妈妈也一定是在雪愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怀着自己的想法努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那个的绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想问他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生抓到那个娃娃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  慢慢来  慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…孝一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能把阿孝带走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也完全没考虑过妈妈的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}喂  我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  快能开店了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是用来当作手信的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自做了决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去伯母那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不打算诱拐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞同过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把喜翠庄的事好好和伯母说一说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能消气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又自以为是地雪愿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.69,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那栋大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么那么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这行李是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  难道是喜翠庄的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还接送  真走运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要带我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然请到假了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想就去泡泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兴趣不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们公司能搞到演唱会的门票哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那么拜托了还拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  请到假了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤乃鹭那边正好可以避暑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么来着  那个新建的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤乃鹭Cirrus吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  那边已经是大人气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不预约就不能入住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄的话永远都是可以临时入住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是能从汤乃鹭Cirrus拿到钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才写了那样的报道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了…别在意那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要好好说一说吗  彻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要来喜翠庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再慢慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起好好喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是喜欢年长的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜欢这个家族的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来啊  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到阿孝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝是指孝一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是绪花的男朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这首也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为谢礼  这个给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是彻先生的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生比预想的要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更正！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就那样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来一支吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是厨师  不能抽烟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真认真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…为什么改变主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就比绪花大没几岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻君真成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被绪花猛猛地训了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像想起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和绪花  说过一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你什么都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈总是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都忍耐着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  比起我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲的工作更伟大些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用什么样的心情去写的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贬低自家的报道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写报道时候没有瞎编乱造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旅馆10年如一日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭想象能写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定是没变化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…追求新颖并不是唯一…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表不管怎么装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的还是本质
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对客人的照料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的细致程度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  妈妈总是做得正确
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得绪花也是挺幸运的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个不总是做得正确的妈妈不也挺好么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  差不多出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花她真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开口就是为喜翠庄的事生气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得还有更应该生气的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去夜逃回到东京却不联系她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直搬来搬去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近终于安稳下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想该联系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花却先自己过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花要回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我一直没想过要回东京呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明东京有阿孝在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算回东京
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也已经不能和阿孝回到以前那样的关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不到了…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在这种时候才摆出母亲的架势
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}让我好好看看这家旅馆的优点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}妈妈也有雪愿！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈还真是轻啊…

